RuntimeContract for UC-112 is intentionally ABSENT in this fixture.

The W8 (sa-uc Runtime Contract phase) decision tree fires "mandatory"
on UC-112 (queue + long-running + recoverable). The expected closed-set
status emitted by sa-uc Phase 4.5 read-back on this UC is:

  Status: BLOCKED
  workflow_detail: runtime_contract_missing

No `.cypher` write block exists. No `RuntimeContract` node. No
`HAS_INITIAL_STATE` / `HAS_TERMINAL_STATE` / `HAS_TRANSITION` /
